graph TB
    subgraph "Notebooks Component - Workbench Images"
        subgraph "Jupyter Images"
            JMinimal[Jupyter Minimal<br/>Python 3.8/3.9]
            JDataSci[Jupyter Data Science<br/>ML Libraries + DB Clients]
            JTensorFlow[Jupyter TensorFlow<br/>Deep Learning]
            JPyTorch[Jupyter PyTorch<br/>CV + NLP]
            JTrustyAI[Jupyter TrustyAI<br/>Model Explainability]
        end

        subgraph "Hardware-Accelerated Images"
            CUDA[CUDA Images<br/>NVIDIA GPU Toolkit]
            Habana[Habana AI Images<br/>Gaudi Accelerators]
            IntelGPU[Intel GPU Images<br/>Intel Acceleration]
        end

        subgraph "Alternative IDEs"
            CodeServer[Code Server<br/>VS Code Browser IDE]
            RStudio[RStudio Server<br/>R IDE]
        end

        subgraph "Pipeline Execution"
            Runtime[Runtime Images<br/>Headless Elyra]
        end

        subgraph "OpenShift Resources"
            ImageStreams[ImageStreams<br/>Version Management N/N-1/N-2]
            ConfigMaps[ConfigMaps<br/>Image Digests + Commits]
        end

        BaseImages[Base Images<br/>UBI8/9, RHEL9, Anaconda]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|selects workbench| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    Dashboard -->|references| ImageStreams
    ImageStreams -->|managed by| NotebookController[Notebook Controller]
    NotebookController -->|creates| StatefulSet[Notebook StatefulSet]

    StatefulSet -->|runs| JMinimal
    StatefulSet -->|runs| JDataSci
    StatefulSet -->|runs| JTensorFlow
    StatefulSet -->|runs| JPyTorch
    StatefulSet -->|runs| CodeServer
    StatefulSet -->|runs| RStudio

    BaseImages -.->|base layer| JMinimal
    JMinimal -.->|extends| JDataSci
    JDataSci -.->|extends| JTensorFlow
    JDataSci -.->|extends| JPyTorch
    JDataSci -.->|extends| JTrustyAI

    BaseImages -.->|base layer| CUDA
    CUDA -.->|GPU variant| JDataSci

    JMinimal -->|sidecar| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy]
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates| User

    JDataSci -->|stores models| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    JDataSci -->|submits pipelines| KFP[Kubeflow Pipelines]
    Runtime -->|executes in| KFP
    JDataSci -->|persists data| S3[S3 Storage]

    ImageStreams -->|pulls from| Quay[quay.io/modh/*]
    ConfigMaps -->|tracks| Quay

    JDataSci -->|installs packages| PyPI[pypi.org]
    JDataSci -->|clones repos| GitHub[github.com]

